es. Whatever the\ndistribution of life in the Universe, observations of terrestrial exoplanets in\ncoming decades will provide a quantitative understanding of the atmospheric\nevolution of lifeless worlds. This knowledge will inform future instrument\nrequirements to either corroborate the presence of life elsewhere or confirm\nits apparent absence.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 21 Feb 2022 16:10:34 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 1 Mar 2022 21:05:38 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-03"}
