rgin. Ablation studies also verify the\neffectiveness of the Instance Relation Transformer encoder and the Multiple\nStructured Knowledge.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Feb 2022 11:32:59 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Sat, 26 Feb 2022 03:01:37 GMT"}],"update_date":"2022-03-01"}
